xalan-c-doc in Fedora 34

This page displays detailed information for a specific version of xalan-c-doc. You might want go back to the main page of xalan-c-doc.

Changelog

Date Author Change
2021-01-27 Fedora Release Engineering - 1.12.0-5 - Rebuilt for https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_34_Mass_Rebuild
2020-12-05 Benjamin A. Beasley - 1.12.0-4 - Make -doc package arch again; there are indeed small differences by architecture. Note that 1.12.0-3 never made it to any buildroot, as the arch differences were flagged by koji.
2020-12-04 Benjamin A. Beasley - 1.12.0-3 - Make -doc package noarch
2020-12-01 Benjamin A. Beasley - 1.12.0-2 - Make spec file compatible with EPEL8: force CMake out-of-source build, add ldconfig_scriptlets macro, and add explicit dependency on graphviz (dot) for API docs
2020-11-30 Benjamin A. Beasley - 1.12.0-1 - New upstream version 1.12.0 - Source code signature verification - New CMake build system - Enable new optional ICU dependency - Build API documentation with Doxygen
2020-08-01 Fedora Release Engineering - 1.11.0-19 - Second attempt - Rebuilt for https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_33_Mass_Rebuild
